OL,3,CCharities warn of 'cat crisis' amid
OL,4,Crise in cats not being neutered
OL,6,FMore than 1,400 cats were in RSPCA
OL,7,Fcare at the end of last year- compared
OL,8,Fto 832 cats that were with the charity
OL,9,Ffour years ago.
OL,11,FThey are urging owners to neuter their
OL,12,Fpets and to stop unwanted breeding,
OL,13,Fwhich exacerbates the problem amid an
OL,14,Fongoing "capacity and welfare crisis".
OL,16,FJo Chambers, Animal Welfare Officer at
OL,17,FMount Noddy animal centre near
OL,18,FChichester, says this is a growing
OL,19,Fproblem.
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
