PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772471476
OL,3,CCharities warn of 'cat crisis' amid
OL,4,Crise in cats not being neutered
OL,6,FShe said: "We are creating a bit of a
OL,7,Fcat crisis at the moment because of
OL,8,Fthis.
OL,10,F"Nowadays we are seeing more and more
OL,11,Fof what we call multi-cat households,
OL,12,Fwhere you have lots and lots of cats
OL,13,Fliving in a very small house together,
OL,14,Fmaybe where breeding has just got
OL,15,Fcompletely out of control.
OL,17,FNeutering is an operation to prevent
OL,18,Ffemale cats as young as four months
OL,19,Fold from getting pregnant and males
OL,20,Ffrom reproducing, but it also keeps
OL,21,Fthem happy and healthy.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
