PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772471476
OL,3,CCharities warn of 'cat crisis' amid
OL,4,Crise in cats not being neutered
OL,6,FOut of the 240 cats adopted by RSPCA
OL,7,FMount Noddy animal centre last year,
OL,8,F194 of them weren't neutered when they
OL,9,Farrived and the charity had to do the
OL,10,Foperation before re-homing them.
OL,12,FJo explained there is help available
OL,13,Fto those who are struggling
OL,14,Ffinancially: "There are a couple of
OL,15,Fthings we run here at the centre to
OL,16,Fhelp: One is a trap neutral scheme,
OL,17,Fwhich is a TNR scheme, and that's for
OL,18,Fwhen you might have a group of cats
OL,19,Fliving somewhere safe, for example.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772471476
OL,3,CCharities warn of 'cat crisis' amid
OL,4,Crise in cats not being neutered
OL,6,F"Someone might be at a farm or barn or
OL,7,Fstables might be feeding a small group
OL,8,Fof cats and we don't want that group
OL,9,Fof 5 or 6 cats to be having up of 3 or
OL,10,F4 litters a year.
OL,12,F"The other scheme we run is for low
OL,13,Fincome pet owners in our branch area
OL,14,Fand you can apply for that on our
OL,15,Fwebsite under neuter voucher scheme.
OL,16,FWe ask for a small donation towards
OL,17,Fthe neuter voucher."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772471476
OL,3,CCharities warn of 'cat crisis' amid
OL,4,Crise in cats not being neutered
OL,6,FThe charity hopes that by raising
OL,7,Fawareness about the importance of
OL,8,Fneutering, it can help stem the surge
OL,9,Fin unwanted pets.
OL,11,FAlice Potter, cat welfare expert at
OL,12,Fthe RSPCA, said: "The rising numbers
OL,13,Fof cats and kittens coming into our
OL,14,Fcare is heartbreaking - and especially
OL,15,Fworrying in the winter months. Many
OL,16,Fare dumped or are kittens born in
OL,17,Funsafe situations as part of a feral
OL,18,Fgroup.
OL,26,@tD@ROU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772471476
OL,3,CCharities warn of 'cat crisis' amid
OL,4,Crise in cats not being neutered
OL,6,F"But owners can really do their bit to
OL,7,Fhelp with the capacity and welfare
OL,8,Fcrisis. Cat owners who neuter their
OL,9,Fcats help stem this surge in unwanted
OL,10,Fpets.
OL,12,F"There is a misconception that cats
OL,13,Fcan only become pregnant when they are
OL,14,Folder or that it's healthy for them to
OL,15,Fhave at least one litter of kittens
OL,16,Fbut this isn't the case - cats can
OL,17,Fbecome pregnant as young as four
OL,18,Fmonths of age, so neutering at this
OL,19,Fage is crucial.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772471476
OL,3,CCharities warn of 'cat crisis' amid
OL,4,Crise in cats not being neutered
OL,6,F"Neutering male cats can stop them
OL,7,Fspraying to mark territory, and from
OL,8,Fgetting injuries while fighting.
OL,9,FNeutered cats are also less likely to
OL,10,Fwander as far. Having them snipped can
OL,11,Falso stop cats from spreading the FIV
OL,12,FVirus - which is spread through cat
OL,13,Fbites, often between male cats
OL,14,Ffighting over a mate."
OL,16,FAccording to the charity Cats
OL,17,FProtection, there are 11 million owned
OL,18,Fcats in the UK - of those a whopping
OL,19,F12% are not neutered - that's around
OL,20,F1.3million cats.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
