FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772471476
OL,3,CCharities warn of 'cat crisis' amid
OL,4,Crise in cats not being neutered
OL,6,FThe top reasons given for not
OL,7,Fneutering include that the cat does
OL,8,Fnot go outside, the owner wants to
OL,9,Fhave kittens, and the owner thinks the
OL,10,Fcat is too young.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
